0:00:00.000,0:00:04.080
Please, Man of God, help me! I cannot walk due to a fractured femur.

0:00:04.080,0:00:06.020
For one year now, I cannot do anything on my own.

0:00:06.020,0:00:08.060
I cannot walk; I cannot go to my workplace.

0:00:08.060,0:00:10.480
I cannot even take a bath without the help of my wife.

0:00:10.480,0:00:12.380
Please, Man of God, help me!

0:00:12.380,0:00:39.120
Healing In Jesus' Name

0:00:39.120,0:00:42.800
Stand up. Don't run, walk gently.

0:00:42.800,0:00:47.020
Healed In Jesus' Name

0:00:47.020,0:00:52.360
Thank You, Jesus; I'm free!

0:00:52.360,0:00:55.700
Thank You, Jesus; I can walk now!

0:00:55.700,0:01:00.260
TESTIMONY TIME

0:01:00.260,0:01:05.560
My name is Joshua Sunday Oladele.

0:01:05.560,0:01:12.880
The lady beside me is my beautiful wife.

0:01:12.880,0:01:20.700
What brought me to The SCOAN was a fracture of the femur.

0:01:20.700,0:01:24.080
It happened in 2014.

0:01:24.080,0:01:31.260
To the glory of God, I came here in 2015, met the man of God who laid hands on me and prayed for me.

0:01:31.260,0:01:38.680
I stood up and since then, I began to walk.

0:01:38.680,0:01:44.440
Before coming to The SCOAN, I had tried many places.

0:01:44.440,0:01:49.320
The very first day the accident happened, I was taken to the hospital.

0:01:49.320,0:01:52.120
I also went to a herbalist and stayed at his place for three months.

0:01:52.120,0:01:59.700
After three months, he asked me to go and buy crutches to be using for walking. I would be okay.

0:01:59.700,0:02:01.780
I bought the crutches, and I left that place.

0:02:01.780,0:02:07.000
When I got home, I realised that the bone was not joined.

0:02:07.000,0:02:10.860
So I went to another herbalist.

0:02:10.860,0:02:13.480
In fact, I tried so many herbalists.

0:02:13.480,0:02:16.660
At the end of the day, we realised that this situation was not ordinary.

0:02:16.660,0:02:20.180
We started moving from church to church for deliverance.

0:02:20.180,0:02:22.400
Still, there was no solution.

0:02:22.400,0:02:25.580
God finally directed me to The SCOAN.

0:02:25.580,0:02:27.580
I was opportune to meet the man of God.

0:02:27.580,0:02:33.520
Immediately he touched me, I stood up and walked.

0:02:33.520,0:02:35.960
Before, I could not go to my working place.

0:02:35.960,0:02:38.560
I even lost my job during the period I had the problem

0:02:38.560,0:02:42.620
because the accident did not happen during working hours,

0:02:42.620,0:02:47.940
When they expected me to return to work in time and they saw that I could not resume back to my duty,

0:02:47.940,0:02:52.420
they sent my payoff to me.

0:02:52.420,0:02:56.800
It was very difficult to feed because I was the breadwinner of the family.

0:02:56.800,0:02:59.120
I could not go to work.

0:02:59.120,0:03:02.440
My wife was the one taking care of me.

0:03:02.440,0:03:08.300
I couldn't even take my bath or go to the toilet by myself.

0:03:08.300,0:03:10.960
In fact, it was very  difficult.

0:03:10.960,0:03:15.460
But after the prayer of Prophet T.B. Joshua, you are able to do all those things you could not do then.

0:03:15.460,0:03:22.720
After the prayer of Prophet T.B. Joshua, for the very first time, I stood up and walked without crutches.

0:03:22.720,0:03:26.480
Ok, there is one thing we want to ask you.

0:03:26.480,0:03:31.780
What was happening to you when the man of God was praying for you because we saw your leg moving?

0:03:31.780,0:03:35.120
Tell us - what were you feeling then as the man of God was praying for you?

0:03:35.120,0:03:40.140
When man of God tapped my leg, I felt heat.

0:03:40.140,0:03:44.040
When he asked me to stand up, I felt as if something fell down from my leg.

0:03:44.040,0:03:51.720
I felt a ring, something - I sensed that something dropped from my leg.

0:03:51.720,0:03:53.340
He then asked me to move.

0:03:53.340,0:03:54.760
That was how I began to walk.

0:03:54.760,0:04:00.840
Let's put our hands together for the miracle working Jesus!

0:04:00.840,0:04:04.780
With what the Lord has done in your life, setting you free from that problem,

0:04:04.780,0:04:09.260
what word of advice do you have for people listening to you all around the world?

0:04:09.260,0:04:17.400
My word of advice to viewers all around the world and everybody watching me right now is that

0:04:17.400,0:04:20.960
we should have faith in God.

0:04:20.960,0:04:26.460
Just as the man of God always says,  when you have a problem, you should come to God,

0:04:26.460,0:04:28.980
don't run away from God.

0:04:28.980,0:04:38.140
In my case, it was when I came to The SCOAN that I received my healing without paying a penny or naira.

0:04:38.140,0:04:44.060
At the other places that I went to before, I spent a lot of money - some would charge me 50,000 naira,

0:04:44.060,0:04:49.020
at the very first place they charged me 80,000 naira, the second 50,000 naira, some 40,000 naira.

0:04:49.020,0:04:54.600
So what you are telling us is that when you came to The SCOAN, and God used Prophet T.B. Joshua

0:04:54.600,0:04:59.160
to pray for you in the name of Jesus Christ and you were set you free, no money was collected from you?

0:04:59.160,0:05:02.540
No money was collected from me. It was free of charge.

0:05:02.540,0:05:05.940
Let's put our hands together for the Lord Jesus Christ.

0:05:05.940,0:05:07.440
Let's hear from your wife.

0:05:07.440,0:05:10.920
Emmanuel!
(God with Us - Matthew 1:23)

0:05:10.920,0:05:17.780
My name is Temitope Oladele. The man standing beside me is my husband.

0:05:17.780,0:05:23.620
I thank God today because I'm very happy.

0:05:23.620,0:05:31.220
When we came here two years ago and met Prophet T.B. Joshua here,

0:05:31.220,0:05:35.700
he prayed for my husband and my husband walked instantly.

0:05:35.700,0:05:37.320
I am very happy.

0:05:37.320,0:05:41.680
It wasn't easy because I was the only one helping him

0:05:41.680,0:05:48.280
and taking care of the children as well as providing food. It was me that was doing everything.

0:05:48.280,0:05:53.440
- But after the prayer and he was set free, he can do everything on his own.
- Yes.

0:05:53.440,0:05:55.560
- And you are very happy about that.
- Yes.

0:05:55.560,0:05:58.160
We thank God Almighty for what the Lord has done in your life.

0:05:58.160,0:06:02.340
Can you just exercise your body and let the people see what the Lord has done for you -

0:06:02.340,0:06:05.000
those things you could not do then.

0:06:05.000,0:06:07.560
Then I couldn't stand and walk like this.

0:06:07.560,0:06:16.220
But now, I can stand on this leg, I can move and run.

0:06:16.220,0:06:18.040
Glory be to God in the highest.

